---
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
import imgClient from '@images/testimonials/miduk.png';
import clientA from '@images/clients/redtop.webp';
import clientB from '@images/clients/stregis.webp';
import clientC from '@images/clients/bidakara.webp';
---

<!-- Testimonials with Stats -->
<div class="max-w-[85rem] px-4 py-20 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 lg:py-20 mx-auto">
  <!-- Grid -->
  <div class="text-base lg:grid lg:grid-cols-12 lg:items-center lg:justify-between lg:gap-16">
    <div class="lg:col-span-5 lg:col-start-1">
      <!-- Title -->
      <div class="mb-8">
        <h2
          class="font-heading mb-2 text-3xl font-bold text-gray-800 lg:text-4xl dark:text-neutral-200"
        >
          It's all about speed
        </h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-neutral-400">
          Respons cepat, solusi tepat. Kami selesaikan masalah Anda tanpa menunggu lama.
        </p>
      </div>
      <!-- End Title -->

      <!-- Blockquote -->
      <blockquote class="relative">
        <svg
          class="absolute start-0 top-0 size-16 -translate-x-6 -translate-y-8 transform text-gray-200 dark:text-neutral-800"
          width="16"
          height="16"
          viewBox="0 0 16 16"
          fill="none"
          xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
          aria-hidden="true"
        >
          <path
            d="M7.39762 10.3C7.39762 11.0733 7.14888 11.7 6.6514 12.18C6.15392 12.6333 5.52552 12.86 4.76621 12.86C3.84979 12.86 3.09047 12.5533 2.48825 11.94C1.91222 11.3266 1.62421 10.4467 1.62421 9.29999C1.62421 8.07332 1.96459 6.87332 2.64535 5.69999C3.35231 4.49999 4.33418 3.55332 5.59098 2.85999L6.4943 4.25999C5.81354 4.73999 5.26369 5.27332 4.84476 5.85999C4.45201 6.44666 4.19017 7.12666 4.05926 7.89999C4.29491 7.79332 4.56983 7.73999 4.88403 7.73999C5.61716 7.73999 6.21938 7.97999 6.69067 8.45999C7.16197 8.93999 7.39762 9.55333 7.39762 10.3ZM14.6242 10.3C14.6242 11.0733 14.3755 11.7 13.878 12.18C13.3805 12.6333 12.7521 12.86 11.9928 12.86C11.0764 12.86 10.3171 12.5533 9.71484 11.94C9.13881 11.3266 8.85079 10.4467 8.85079 9.29999C8.85079 8.07332 9.19117 6.87332 9.87194 5.69999C10.5789 4.49999 11.5608 3.55332 12.8176 2.85999L13.7209 4.25999C13.0401 4.73999 12.4903 5.27332 12.0713 5.85999C11.6786 6.44666 11.4168 7.12666 11.2858 7.89999C11.5215 7.79332 11.7964 7.73999 12.1106 7.73999C12.8437 7.73999 13.446 7.97999 13.9173 8.45999C14.3886 8.93999 14.6242 9.55333 14.6242 10.3Z"
            fill="currentColor"></path>
        </svg>

        <div class="relative z-10">
          <p class="text-base text-gray-800 italic dark:text-white">
            " Tim sales sangat responsif, jelas dalam menjelaskan solusi yang ditawarkan, serta
            fleksibel dalam penjadwalan sesuai dengan kebutuhan operasional pabrik kami. "
          </p>
        </div>

        <footer class="mt-6">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-x-4">
            <div class="shrink-0">
              {
                (
                  <Image
                    src={imgClient}
                    alt="Miduk Lasman - PT. Modelez Indonesia Manufacturing"
                    class="size-8 rounded-full"
                    draggable="false"
                    loading="lazy"
                    format="avif"
                  />
                )
              }
            </div>
            <div class="grow">
              <div class="font-semibold text-gray-800 dark:text-neutral-200">Miduk Lasman</div>
              <div class="text-xs text-gray-500 dark:text-neutral-500">
                Project Engineer & Automation Lead | PT. MondelÄ“z Indonesia Manufacturing
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </footer>
      </blockquote>
      <!-- End Blockquote -->
    </div>
    <!-- End Col -->

    <div class="mt-10 lg:col-span-6 lg:col-end-13 lg:mt-0">
      <div class="space-y-6 sm:space-y-8">
        <!-- List -->
        <ul
          class="grid grid-cols-2 divide-x divide-y divide-gray-200 overflow-hidden dark:divide-neutral-700"
        >
          <li class="-m-0.5 flex flex-col p-4 sm:p-8">
            <div
              class="mb-2 flex items-end gap-x-2 text-3xl font-bold text-gray-800 sm:text-5xl dark:text-neutral-200"
            >
              10k+
            </div>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 sm:text-base dark:text-neutral-400">
              pekerjaan dilakukan dengan cepat, tepat, dan profesional
            </p>
          </li>

          <li class="-m-0.5 flex flex-col p-4 sm:p-8">
            <div
              class="mb-2 flex items-end gap-x-2 text-3xl font-bold text-gray-800 sm:text-5xl dark:text-neutral-200"
            >
              70%
            </div>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 sm:text-base dark:text-neutral-400">
              sudah bermitra lebih dari 5 tahun
            </p>
          </li>

          <li class="-m-0.5 flex flex-col p-4 sm:p-8">
            <div
              class="mb-2 flex items-end gap-x-2 text-3xl font-bold text-gray-800 sm:text-5xl dark:text-neutral-200"
            >
              99.5%
            </div>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 sm:text-base dark:text-neutral-400">
              Tingkat retensi pelanggan kembali dalam 3 bulan.
            </p>
          </li>

          <li class="-m-0.5 flex flex-col p-4 sm:p-8">
            <div
              class="mb-2 flex items-end gap-x-2 text-3xl font-bold text-gray-800 sm:text-5xl dark:text-neutral-200"
            >
              24/7
            </div>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 sm:text-base dark:text-neutral-400">
              layanan dukungan - kami selalu siap membantu
            </p>
          </li>
        </ul>
        <!-- End List -->
      </div>
    </div>
    <!-- End Col -->
  </div>
  <!-- End Grid -->
</div>
<!-- End Testimonials with Stats -->
<!-- Testimonials -->
<div class="mx-auto max-w-[85rem] px-4 pb-16 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 lg:pb-16">
  <!-- Grid -->
  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-6 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3">
    <!-- Card -->
    <div
      class="flex flex-col rounded-xl border border-gray-200 bg-white shadow-2xs dark:border-neutral-700 dark:bg-neutral-900"
    >
      <div class="flex-auto p-4 md:p-6">
        {
          (
            <Image
              src={clientA}
              alt="Redtop Hotel Jakarta"
              class="h-8 w-auto"
              draggable="false"
              loading="lazy"
              format="avif"
            />
          )
        }

        <p class="mt-3 text-base text-gray-800 sm:mt-6 dark:text-white">
          <em>
            " Sejak menggunakan jasa Ecofix, permasalahan tersebut dapat dikendalikan dengan baik.
            Tim teknisi datang dengan perlengkapan lengkap, sangat disiplin soal waktu, dan rapi
            dalam bekerja. "
          </em>
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="rounded-b-xl p-4 md:px-6">
        <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-gray-800 sm:text-base dark:text-neutral-200">
          Richard
        </h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-neutral-500">
          Spv. Engineering | Redtop Hotel Jakarta
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <!-- End Card -->

    <!-- Card -->
    <div
      class="flex flex-col rounded-xl border border-gray-200 bg-white shadow-2xs dark:border-neutral-700 dark:bg-neutral-900"
    >
      <div class="flex-auto p-4 md:p-6">
        {
          (
            <Image
              src={clientB}
              alt="St. Regis Hotels & Resorts Jakarta"
              class="h-auto w-20"
              draggable="false"
              loading="lazy"
              format="avif"
            />
          )
        }

        <p class="mt-3 text-base text-gray-800 sm:mt-6 dark:text-white">
          <em>
            " Kami sangat terbantu dengan layanan Ecofix.id untuk membersihkan perangkap minyak
            secara berkala di dapur hotel kami. Hasil kerja petugasnya rapi, tidak mengganggu
            operasional dapur, dan sangat komunikatif dalam memberikan edukasi. "
          </em>
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="rounded-b-xl p-4 md:px-6">
        <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-gray-800 sm:text-base dark:text-neutral-200">
          Mochamad Era
        </h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-neutral-500">
          Engineering Manager | St. Regis Hotels & Resorts
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <!-- End Card -->

    <!-- Card -->
    <div
      class="flex flex-col rounded-xl border border-gray-200 bg-white shadow-2xs dark:border-neutral-700 dark:bg-neutral-900"
    >
      <div class="flex-auto p-4 md:p-6">
        {
          (
            <Image
              src={clientC}
              alt="Hotel Bidakara Jakarta"
              class="h-auto w-20"
              draggable="false"
              loading="lazy"
              format="avif"
            />
          )
        }

        <p class="mt-3 text-base text-gray-800 sm:mt-6 dark:text-white">
          <em>
            " Sudah lebih dari 10 tahun kami mempercayakan pekerjaan Grease Trap dan Drain Cleaning
            kepada tim Ecofix.id. Sejak menggunakan layanan Ecofix, semua masalah bisa teratasi
            dengan sangat baik. "
          </em>
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="rounded-b-xl p-4 md:px-6">
        <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-gray-800 sm:text-base dark:text-neutral-200">Lia</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-neutral-500">
          Adm. Engineering | Hotel Bidakara Jakarta
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <!-- End Card -->
  </div>
  <!-- End Grid -->
</div>
<!-- End Testimonials -->
